    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for a fantastic ride! This well-maintained vehicle is in good condition and has been cared for to ensure it\u2019s ready for its next owner. It offers a smooth, reliable driving experience with plenty of life left in it\u2014a perfect choice for someone looking for a dependable and attractive car that's ready to go!",
